<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ZUNGZAL IN KAN THANGTHAT KO LAI</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zungzal in Bawipa kan thangthat ko lai
 Tingtang le hladawh in kan thangthat lai,
 Zungzal in Bawipa kan thangthat ko lai
 Harnak le ngeihchiatnak ton caan zong ah.

[B1]
   Kut thlir buin, kan thangthat lai
   Lunglawm tein, kan thangthat lai,

[C1]
   Ka nunnak ka thlarau ka zeizong tein
   Bawipa nang cu zungzal kan thangthat lai
   A thiang bikmi, Pa Pathian,
   Ka ningzahnak ralchiatnak kaltak dih in
   Bawipa nang cu zungzal kan thangthat lai
   A thiang bikmi, pa Pathian.

[B2]
   Halleluijah, Halleluijah
   Halleluijah, Halleluijah.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
</song>